title: Low Methane Emissions from Industrial Processes
description: In 2023, the Philippines reported a minimal methane emission of 0.0001 Mt CO2e from industrial processes, showcasing its commitment to reducing greenhouse gases.

title: High Women's HIV Prevalence
description: As of 2022, 6.63% of women aged 15 and above in the Philippines were living with HIV, indicating a significant public health challenge.

title: Low Wanted Fertility Rate
description: The wanted fertility rate in the Philippines was 1.5 births per woman in 2022, reflecting a potential shift towards smaller family sizes.

title: Dominance in Medium and High-Tech Exports
description: In 2022, 80.02% of the Philippines' manufactured exports were medium and high-tech, highlighting its strong position in the global tech market.
